in two days of picketing the hollywood 
teamsters strike has accomplished what scriptwriters failed to 
achieve over five months in their walkout the shutdown of a studio 
citing death threats bomb scares and sabotaged equipment 
cannell studios said tuesday it has halted production on its 
television shows hunter and sonny spoon 
it said the incidents were related to the strike by 3200 
drivers laborers and electricians and that production would resume 
work only when it is safe 
in a separate incident one picket was arrested for battery 
tuesday morning at universal studios said police lt ron young 
