stock market crash 
as a result of the crash 28 percent of the total respondents 
and 48 percent of the stockholders said they had made changes in 
the way they handle their finances such as making more 
conservative investments or saving more 
seventytwo percent of the total sample and 52 percent of the 
stockholders said they had made no changes 
